sentence.text: Mutations in eight of them (ubiquinone biosynthetic process, PDSS2, ubiquinone biosynthetic process, ubiquinone biosynthetic process, ubiquinone biosynthetic process, ADCK3, ADCK4, and COQ9) cause primary CoQ(10) deficiency, a heterogeneous group of disorders with variable age of onset (from birth to the seventh decade) and associated clinical phenotypes, ranging from a fatal multisystem disease to isolated steroid resistant nephrotic syndrome (SRNS) or isolated central nervous system disease.
